                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成6点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素伤害</span>；如果<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">璇玑屏</span>在场，就使此伤害+2。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/03/47826599/55dfd3944aa4091c2684c17412739558_3987655516656919890.png",
